line: EYECATCH DC    CL32'*** PROGRAM ASAM1 DATA AREAS ***'
FILECC   DC    H'0'                  MAX RETURN CODE FROM FILE OPENS
data_type: H'0'                  MAX RETURN CODE FROM FILE OPENS

line: RECCOUNT DC    PL4'0'                INPUT RECORD COUNT
STATUS   DC    CL30' '               CURRENT PROGRAM STATUS
EOFFLAG  DC    XL1'00'               END OF INPUT FILE FLAG
data_type: XL1'00'               END OF INPUT FILE FLAG

line: RETCODE  DC    F'0'                  DEFAULT RETURN CODE IS ZERO
data_type: F'0'                  DEFAULT RETURN CODE IS ZERO

line: Alignfull    DS       0F            align full word boundary
Var1         DS       HL20          var1 length is 20
Var2         DC       CL10'ABCDE FGHI'    var2 length is 5
